From: Takeshi Kihara <takeshi.kihara.df@renesas.com>
Date: Fri, 16 Feb 2018 15:25:03 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] pinctrl: sh-pfc: r8a7796: Fix MOD_SEL register pin assignment
 for SSI pins group
References: bnc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 4.16.13
Git-commit: b418c4609d5052d174668ad6d13efe023c45c595

[ Upstream commit b418c4609d5052d174668ad6d13efe023c45c595 ]

This patch fixes MOD_SEL1 bit20 and MOD_SEL2 bit20, bit21 pin assignment
for SSI pins group.

This is a correction to the incorrect implementation of MOD_SEL register
pin assignment for R8A7796 SoC specification of R-Car Gen3 Hardware
User's Manual Rev.0.51E or later.

